title: All Right
description: welcome to my debut sound.xyz drop. If you like tom misch, cory wong, galantis, fred again.., great good fine okay, etc. there's something here for you. 'all right' incorporates a lot of musical elements that feel authentically me. intricate guitar parts, glitchy drums, lush chords.

title: Half Life - Green Ring Remix
description:
A Message From Green Ring:
‘Half Life’ has such a cool story and meaning in Rosalie’s journey, so I was honored when she asked me to put together a remix. The song mostly came together in the very first session as the original has some incredible material to work with. I just tried to bring the song into my own world by adding some new sounds and letting the idea flow freely. Really happy with how it turned out. I hope you enjoy, and thank you for listening.

title: be with u
description: "be with u" is an emotional indie dance/future house fusion and is my first release of 2024. It features a heartfelt refrain, "always wanna be with u," dancing around warm, organic synths and deep basses, crafting a love-infused number. Evolving four-on-the-floor drums add rhythmic flair, and playful vocal chops in the later sections enhance the emotional resonance. This song encapsulates the enduring essence of love, offering a melodic embrace for those moments of heartfelt connection on the dance floor.
